<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="addicted-adj">addicted <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /əˈdɪktɪd/    美 /əˈdɪktɪd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>上瘾的；入迷的：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>(be) addicted to (doing) sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He admits that recently he has become addicted to playing online games.
他承认最近他沉迷于玩网络游戏。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Some students become addicted to the Internet and cannot concentrate on school and family life.
一些学生沉迷于网络，无法专注于学业和家庭生活。</p><footer>人教新必修①-1改</footer></div></div>